➜降维打击实锤？搭载3.5L+V6发动机，东风悦达起亚MPV嘉华正式公布
http://www.sohu.com/a/421074265_99994080	53293
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200926/fcffaff3b1454762ac5b7470a3607f4f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200926/aa15087d5ec1454a8c1edf0149405219.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>本文编辑：</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200926/ce574d90ada94d39a7fd2f3fb39f3b2d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>写在前面：</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
